82 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
83 VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser(const VContainer *data, QDockWidget *parent)
84  : QObject(parent)
85  , m_data(data)
86  , propertyModel(nullptr)
87  , formView(nullptr)
88  , currentItem(nullptr)
89  , propertyToId(QMap<VPE::VProperty *, QString>())
90  , idToProperty(QMap<QString, VPE::VProperty *>())
91  , m_centerPointStr(tr("Center point"))
92 {
93  propertyModel = new VPE::VPropertyModel(this);
94  formView = new VPE::VPropertyFormView(propertyModel, parent);
95  formView->setSizePolicy(QSizePolicy::Expanding, QSizePolicy::Expanding);
96 
97  QScrollArea *scroll = new QScrollArea(parent);
98  scroll->setWidgetResizable(true);
99  scroll->setWidget(formView);
100 
101  parent->setWidget(scroll);
102 
103  connect(propertyModel, &VPE::VPropertyModel::onDataChangedByEditor, this,
104  &VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::userChangedData);
105 }

384  }
385

504 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
505 void VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::itemClicked(QGraphicsItem *item)
506 {
507  if (item != nullptr)
508  {
509  if (item->isEnabled()==false)
510  {
511  return;
512  }
513 
514  if(item->type() == QGraphicsItem::UserType + static_cast<int>(Tool::BackgroundImage))
515  {
516  item = nullptr;
517  }
518  }
519 
520  if (currentItem == item && item != nullptr)
521  {
522  updateOptions();
523  return;
524  }
525 
526  propertyModel->clear();
527  propertyToId.clear();
528  idToProperty.clear();
529 
530  if (currentItem != nullptr)
531  {
532  VAbstractTool *previousTool = dynamic_cast<VAbstractTool *>(currentItem);
533  if (previousTool != nullptr)
534  {
535  previousTool->ShowVisualization(false); // hide for previous tool
536  }
537  }
538 
539  currentItem = item;
540  if (currentItem == nullptr)
541  {
542  formView->setTitle("");
543  return;
544  }
545 
546  showItemOptions(currentItem);
547 }

567 }

682 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
683 template<class Tool>
684 void VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::addPropertyLineType(Tool *tool, const QString &propertyName)
685 {
686  VPE::LineTypeProperty *lineTypeProperty = new VPE::LineTypeProperty(propertyName);
687 
688  QMap<QString, QString> lineTypes = lineTypeList();
689  if (tool->type() == VToolLine::Type)
690  {
691  lineTypes.remove(LineTypeNone);
692  }
693  lineTypeProperty->setLineTypes(lineTypes);
694 
695  const qint32 index = VPE::LineTypeProperty::indexOfLineType(lineTypes, tool->getLineType());
696  if (index == -1)
697  {
698  qWarning() << "Can't find line type" << tool->getLineType() << "in list";
699  }
700  lineTypeProperty->setValue(index);
701  addProperty(lineTypeProperty, AttrLineType);
702 }

766 template<class Tool>
767 QMap<QString, quint32> VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::getObjectList(Tool *tool, GOType objType)
768 {
769  quint32 toolId = tool->getId();
770  QHash<quint32, QSharedPointer<VGObject>> objects;
771 
772  QVector<VToolRecord> history = qApp->getCurrentDocument()->getBlockHistory();
773  for (qint32 i = 0; i < history.size(); ++i)
774  {
775  const VToolRecord record = history.at(i);
776  quint32 recId = record.getId();
777  if (recId != toolId)
778  {
779  switch (static_cast<int>(record.getTypeTool()))
780  {
781  case 42: //Tool::True Darts
782  {
783  QVector<quint32> list = qApp->getCurrentDocument()->getDartItems(recId);
784  for (qint32 j = 0; j < list.size(); ++j)
785  {
786  quint32 id = list.at(j);
787  VToolRecord newRecord = VToolRecord(id, record.getTypeTool(),
788  qApp->getCurrentDocument()->getActiveDraftBlockName());
789 
790  const QHash<quint32, QSharedPointer<VGObject> > *objs = m_data->DataGObjects();
791  if (objs->contains(id)) //Avoid badId Get GObject only if not a line tool which is not an object
792  {
793  QSharedPointer<VGObject> obj = m_data->GetGObject(id);
794  objects.insert(id, obj);
795  }
796  }
797  break;
798  }
799 
800  case 45: //Tool::Rotation
801  case 46: //Tool::MirrorByLine
802  case 47: //Tool::MirrorByAxis
803  case 48: //Tool::Move
804  {
805  QVector<quint32> list = qApp->getCurrentDocument()->getOpItems(recId, QStringLiteral("destination"));
806  for (qint32 j = 0; j < list.size(); ++j)
807  {
808  quint32 id = list.at(j);
809  VToolRecord newRecord = VToolRecord(id, record.getTypeTool(),
810  qApp->getCurrentDocument()->getActiveDraftBlockName());
811 
812  const QHash<quint32, QSharedPointer<VGObject> > *objs = m_data->DataGObjects();
813  if (objs->contains(id)) //Avoid badId Get GObject only if not a line tool which is not an object
814  {
815  QSharedPointer<VGObject> obj = m_data->GetGObject(id);
816  objects.insert(id, obj);
817  }
818  }
819  break;
820  }
821  default:
822  {
823  const QHash<quint32, QSharedPointer<VGObject> > *objs = m_data->DataGObjects();
824  if (objs->contains(recId)) //Avoid badId Get GObject only if not a line tool which is not an object
825  {
826  QSharedPointer<VGObject> obj = m_data->GetGObject(recId);
827  objects.insert(recId, obj);
828  }
829  break;
830  }
831  }
832  }
833  else
834  {
835  goto endLoop; //Copied objects upto selected tool - exit switch and for loops
836  }
837  }
838 
839 endLoop:
840  QMap<QString, quint32> map;
841  QHash<quint32, QSharedPointer<VGObject> >::const_iterator i;
842  for (i = objects.constBegin(); i != objects.constEnd(); ++i)
843  {
844  QSharedPointer<VGObject> obj = i.value();
845  if (obj->getMode() == Draw::Calculation)
846  {
847  switch (objType)
848  {
849  case GOType::Point:
850  case GOType::Arc:
851  case GOType::Spline:
852  case GOType::CubicBezier:
853  case GOType::SplinePath:
854  case GOType::CubicBezierPath:
855  if (obj->getType() == objType)
856  {
857  map.insert(obj->name(), i.key());
858  }
859  break;
860 
861  case GOType::Curve:
862  if (obj->getType() == GOType::Spline || obj->getType() == GOType::CubicBezier)
863  {
864  map.insert(obj->name(), i.key());
865  }
866  break;
867 
868  case GOType::Path:
869  if (obj->getType() == GOType::SplinePath || obj->getType() == GOType::CubicBezierPath)
870  {
871  map.insert(obj->name(), i.key());
872  }
873  break;
874 
875  case GOType::AllCurves:
876  if ((obj->getType() == GOType::Spline ||
877  obj->getType() == GOType::SplinePath ||
878  obj->getType() == GOType::CubicBezier ||
879  obj->getType() == GOType::CubicBezierPath ||
880  obj->getType() == GOType::Arc ||
881  obj->getType() == GOType::EllipticalArc) &&
882  obj->getMode() == Draw::Calculation)
883  {
884  map.insert(obj->name(), i.key());
885  }
886  break;
887 
888  case GOType::EllipticalArc:
889  case GOType::Unknown:
890  default:
891  break;
892  }
893  }
894  }
895 
896  if (tool->type() == VToolMove::Type)
897  {
898  map.insert(m_centerPointStr, NULL_ID);
899  }
900  return map;
901 }

905 void VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::setPointName(const QString &name)
906 {
907  if (Tool *tool = qgraphicsitem_cast<Tool *>(currentItem))

918  }
919  else
920  {
921  tool->setName(name);
922  }
923  }
924  else
925  {
926  qWarning() << "Can't cast item";
927  }
928 }

984 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
985 template<class Tool>
986 void VToolOptionsPropertyBrowser::setOperationSuffix(const QString &suffix)
987 {
988  if (Tool *item = qgraphicsitem_cast<Tool *>(currentItem))
989  {
990  if (suffix == item->Suffix())
991  {
992  return;
993  }
994 
995  if (suffix.isEmpty())
996  {
997  idToProperty[AttrSuffix]->setValue(item->Suffix());
998  return;
999  }
1000 
1001  QRegularExpression rx(NameRegExp());
1002  const QStringList uniqueNames = VContainer::AllUniqueNames();
1003  for (int i=0; i < uniqueNames.size(); ++i)
1004  {
1005  const QString name = uniqueNames.at(i) + suffix;
1006  if (not rx.match(name).hasMatch() || not VContainer::IsUnique(name))
1007  {
1008  idToProperty[AttrSuffix]->setValue(item->Suffix());
1009  return;
1010  }
1011  }
1012 
1013  item->setSuffix(suffix);
1014  }
1015  else
1016  {
1017  qWarning() << "Can't cast item";
1018  }
1019 }

1033  case 0:
1034  case 1:
1035  cross = static_cast<Type>(val+1);

1037  default:
1038  break;
1039  }
1040  }
1041 
1042  return cross;

1896 //---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1903 
1904  VToolSpline *tool = qgraphicsitem_cast<VToolSpline *>(currentItem);
1905  SCASSERT(tool != nullptr)
1906 
1907  auto spl = tool->getSpline();
1908  VPointF point;
1909 
1910  const VFormula f = value.value<VFormula>();
1911 
1912  switch (propertiesList().indexOf(id))
1913  {
1914  case 0: // AttrName
1915  Q_UNREACHABLE();//The attribute is read only

1921  break;
1922  case 7: // AttrSecondPoint
1923  point = *m_data->GeometricObject<VPointF>(value.toInt());
1924  spl.SetP4(point);
1925  tool->setSpline(spl);
1926  break;
1927  case 9: // AttrAngle1
1928  if (not f.error())
1929  {
1930  spl.SetStartAngle(f.getDoubleValue(), f.GetFormula(FormulaType::FromUser));
1931  tool->setSpline(spl);
1932  }
1933  break;
1934  case 10: // AttrAngle2
1935  if (not f.error())
1936  {
1937  spl.SetEndAngle(f.getDoubleValue(), f.GetFormula(FormulaType::FromUser));
1938  tool->setSpline(spl);
1939  }
1940  break;
1941  case 36: // AttrLength1
1942  if (not f.error() && f.getDoubleValue() >= 0)
1943  {
1944  spl.SetC1Length(qApp->toPixel(f.getDoubleValue()), f.GetFormula(FormulaType::FromUser));
1945  tool->setSpline(spl);
1946  }
1947  break;
1948  case 37: // AttrLength2
1949  if (not f.error() && f.getDoubleValue() >= 0)
1950  {
1951  spl.SetC2Length(qApp->toPixel(f.getDoubleValue()), f.GetFormula(FormulaType::FromUser));
1952  tool->setSpline(spl);
1953  }
1954  break;
1955  case 27: // AttrColor
1956  tool->setLineColor(value.toString());
1957  break;
1958  case 59: // AttrPenStyle
1959  tool->SetPenStyle(value.toString());
1960  break;
1961  case 60: // AttrLineWeight
1962  tool->setLineWeight(value.toString());
1963  break;
1964  default:
